# Character sheets (male model.png, female model.png) are
#   referenced from ESM SHOOT/2 charachter sheets/ locally.
# To restore character sheets on a new machine:
#   - Re-download from Higgsfield generate history, or
#   - Re-sync from Nour's local drive
# All planning, status, and decision docs ARE tracked.

